    "contentEn": "# Branding for the Wellara medical brand\n\n_January - February 2024_  \nArt director\n\nThe work is still in progress, with a focus on capturing the brand’s identity and ensuring the designs strike the perfect balance between aesthetics and functionality. Each step of the process is guided by Wellara’s commitment to quality and innovation.\n\n![](https://cdn.nevsky.me/content/images/2026/03/wellara-branding-cv__01.png)![](https://cdn.nevsky.me/content/images/2026/03/wellara-branding-cv__02.png)![](https://cdn.nevsky.me/content/images/2026/03/wellara-branding-cv__03.png)![](https://cdn.nevsky.me/content/images/2026/03/wellara-branding-cv__04.png)![](https://cdn.nevsky.me/content/images/2026/03/wellara-branding-cv__05.png)![](https://cdn.nevsky.me/content/images/2026/03/wellara-branding-cv__06.png)![](https://cdn.nevsky.me/content/images/2026/03/wellara-branding-cv__07.png)![](https://cdn.nevsky.me/content/images/2026/03/wellara-branding-cv__08.png)![](https://cdn.nevsky.me/content/images/2026/03/wellara-branding-cv__09.png)![](https://cdn.nevsky.me/content/images/2026/03/wellara-branding-cv__10.png)![](https://cdn.nevsky.me/content/images/2026/03/wellara-branding-cv__11.png)",
    "contentRu": "# Брендинг для медицинского бренда Wellara\n\n_Январь — Февраль 2024_  \nАрт-директор\n\nThe work is still in progress, with a focus on capturing the brand’s identity and ensuring the designs strike the perfect balance between aesthetics and functionality. Each step of the process is guided by Wellara’s commitment to quality and innovation.\n\n![](https://cdn.nevsky.me/content/images/2026/03/wellara-branding-cv__01.png)![](https://cdn.nevsky.me/content/images/2026/03/wellara-branding-cv__02.png)![](https://cdn.nevsky.me/content/images/2026/03/wellara-branding-cv__03.png)![](https://cdn.nevsky.me/content/images/2026/03/wellara-branding-cv__04.png)![](https://cdn.nevsky.me/content/images/2026/03/wellara-branding-cv__05.png)![](https://cdn.nevsky.me/content/images/2026/03/wellara-branding-cv__06.png)![](https://cdn.nevsky.me/content/images/2026/03/wellara-branding-cv__07.png)![](https://cdn.nevsky.me/content/images/2026/03/wellara-branding-cv__08.png)![](https://cdn.nevsky.me/content/images/2026/03/wellara-branding-cv__09.png)![](https://cdn.nevsky.me/content/images/2026/03/wellara-branding-cv__10.png)![](https://cdn.nevsky.me/content/images/2026/03/wellara-branding-cv__11.png)"
